data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER WILLING TO BUY DOWN LOAN RATE! Comfort, luxury, & space abound in this desirable Brier Creek Country Club home. Featuring a brand-new roof, completely refinished hardwood floors, NEW carpet throughout 2nd level, & an array of updates & upgrades, this home is a haven of elevated living. Nestled within a quiet cul-de-sac, this gem offers the rare inclusion of a basement, making it a truly exceptional find within the community. Once you step through the graceful and inviting front porch into a sunlit 2-story foyer, you will find that the layout effortlessly connects each space, creating a sense of openness & ease. The heart of the home lies in the expansive open-concept kitchen & living area, ideal for gatherings with loved ones. French doors lead to another cozy living space, offering flexibility & versatility for your lifestyle needs. A handsome formal dining area capable of hosting large parties is right off the kitchen. Outside, the deck beckons for outdoor enjoyment, be it al fresco dining or simply basking in the serenity of a lovely, fenced yard replete with mature greenery providing shade, privacy & beauty. A versatile office on the main level offers multiple possibilities, whether as a studio retreat or a tranquil yoga sanctuary, complementing the home's dynamic layout. Upstairs, discover a spacious primary suite with dual walk-in closets, along with four additional bedrooms & a generous bonus space. For those craving even more space for entertainment & leisure, the walk-out basement features a well-appointed kitchen & wet bar, perfectly tailored for seamless hosting. If you're in search of a home that prioritizes comfort & functionality without sacrificing style, or space, look no further than this incredible offering in Brier Creek Country Club. Welcome home!
